sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_include_ae01efa11bb4061062f8ea46624bcbcc
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_atsl_uni.TFM_UniversityUtils</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>TFM_UniversityUtils</name><script><![CDATA[var TFM_UniversityUtils = Class.create();

//Groups
TFM_UniversityUtils.PROFESORES_GROUP = 'dd7dd02b47c3f1100aeaa144846d43b4';

//Tablas
TFM_UniversityUtils.PROFESORES_ASIGNATURA_TABLE = 'x_atsl_uni_profesorado_asignatura';
TFM_UniversityUtils.ASIGNATURA_TABLE = 'x_atsl_uni_asignaturas';

TFM_UniversityUtils.getProfesores = function() {
    var gr = new GlideRecord('sys_user_grmember');
    gr.addQuery('group', TFM_UniversityUtils.PROFESORES_GROUP);
    gr.query();
    var users = '';
    while (gr.next()) {
        users += gr.user.sys_id + ",";
    }
    return "sys_idIN" + users;
};

/*
*/
TFM_UniversityUtils.getProfesoresForAsignatura = function(asignatura) {
	var grProfAsig = new GlideRecord(TFM_UniversityUtils.PROFESORES_ASIGNATURA_TABLE);
	grProfAsig.addQuery('asignatura', asignatura);
	grProfAsig.query();
	var users = '';
	while(grProfAsig.next()) {
		users += grProfAsig.profesor.sys_id + ",";
	}
	return "sys_idIN" + users;
};

TFM_UniversityUtils.getLocationsForAsignatura = function(asignatura) {
	var locations = '';
	var grAsignatura = new GlideRecord(TFM_UniversityUtils.ASIGNATURA_TABLE);
	grAsignatura.get(asignatura);
	if(!gs.nil(grAsignatura)) {
		var grSpaces = new GlideRecord('sn_wsd_core_space');
		grSpaces.addQuery('campus', grAsignatura.estudios.centro_responsable.toString());
		grSpaces.query();
		while(grSpaces.next()) {
			locations += grSpaces.sys_id + ",";
		}
	}
	
	return "sys_idIN" + locations;
};

TFM_UniversityUtils.prototype = {
    initialize: function() {},

    type: 'TFM_UniversityUtils'

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="DELETE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>true</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>true</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>cmn_schedule_span</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>TFM Preven repeat time before end</name><order>50</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/ ) {

    var endDate = current.getDisplayValue('end_date_time');
    var repeatTime = current.getDisplayValue('repeat_until');

    if (!gs.nil(repeatTime)) {

        var endDateGdt = new GlideDateTime(endDate);
        var repeatTimeGdt = new GlideDateTime(repeatTime);

        if (repeatTimeGdt < endDateGdt) {
            gs.addErrorMessage('Repeat until time cannot be before the end time');
			current.setAbortAction(true);
			return;
        }

    }

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>aaron.admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2024-03-08 14:03:50</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>825fdff11bb0461062f8ea46624bcbe6</sys_id><sys_mod_count>4</sys_mod_count><sys_name>TFM Preven repeat time before end</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="University Management" source="x_atsl_uni">4279071d1bac425062f8ea46624bcb4e</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="University Management">4279071d1bac425062f8ea46624bcb4e</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_825fdff11bb0461062f8ea46624bcbe6</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>aaron.admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2024-03-08 14:06:40</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=825fdff11bb0461062f8ea46624bcbe6"/></record_update>
